<para id="fs-id1169596235081">Now that we have graphed lines by using the slope and <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis>-intercept, let’s summarize all the methods we have used to graph lines. See <link target-id="CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_04_05_038"/>.</para>
