<item><span class="token">ⓓ</span> <newline/>
<para id="fs-id1169595339462"><media id="fs-id1169594007893" alt="The figure shows a line graphed on the x y-coordinate plane. The x-axis of the plane represents the variable m and runs from negative 10 to 400. The y-axis of the plane represents the variable C and runs from negative 10 to 300. The line begins at the point (0, 65) and goes through the point (250, 185).">
